snippet.title: DEAD OR ALIVE 6 - New Character "Tamaki" Teaser
snippet.description:
A curious gal stumbles into the DEAD OR ALIVE 6 Arena. Her name? Tamaki. Her fighting style? It's yet to be known. 
Stay tuned for more fighters, as Tamaki makes her way into the DEAD OR ALIVE 6 fighting game universe. 

*Tamaki and Debut costumes are included in Season Pass 4*

DEAD OR ALIVE 6 is available now for purchase on PlayStation 4, Xbox One and Steam for PC
https://teamninja-studio.com/doa6/us/products.html

Try DOA6: Core Fighters FREE!
https://teamninja-studio.com/doa6/us/corefighters.html

[official twitter] https://twitter.com/DOATEC_OFFICIAL
